al&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[ to go directly to the Quote Management dialog and update the affected quotes.]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_numbering_level&C1&B/para_numbering_level&C&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&Bitem type = &Epara_start&E/&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[Quotes with a status of Accepted or Rejected are not included in expiry warnings as they have already been resolved.]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_numbering_level&C1&B/para_numbering_level&C&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E14&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Ehaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&Bitem type = &Epara_start&E/&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E14&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Ehaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[5.5 Deleting a Quote]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_numbering_level&C1&B/para_numbering_level&C&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&Bitem type = &Epara_start&E/&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[T