e_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&Bitem type = &Epara_start&E/&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[Symptom:]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[ The generated PDF has different formatting or layout compared to what was shown in the preview window.]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&Bitem type = &Epara_start&E/&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[Solution:]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[ Minor differences between the screen preview and the PDF are normal due to the way Qt renders HTML on screen versus to a PDF file. If the differences are significant &A#x2014; for example sections are missing or the layout is badly wrong &A#x2014; contact PB Software Solutions with a description of the issue.]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaa