l=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[Clicking Send opens a browser instead of my email application]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&Bitem type = &Epara_start&E/&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[Symptom:]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[ After clicking Send in the Email Quote dialog a web browser opens instead of an email application.]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&Bitem type = &Epara_start&E/&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[Solution:]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[ This occurs when no default email application is configured in Windows. Quote Generation will display your email details and the PDF location so you can send the email manually through your webmail. To set a default email application go to Windows ]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Ehaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[Settings &A#x2192; Apps &A#x2192; Default Apps]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[ and set your preferred email application.]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Ehaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&Bitem type = &Epara_start&E/&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Ehaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[The email is sent but the PDF is not attached]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&Bitem type = &Epara_start&E/&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[Symptom:]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[ The email arrives at the recipient but without the PDF attached.]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaa