/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&Bitem type = &Epara_start&E/&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[Symptom:]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[ The Trial Expired dialog appears even though you have purchased a licence.]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&Bitem type = &Epara_start&E/&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[Solution:]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[ Enter your licence key in the Licence Key field of the Trial Expired dialog and click ]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Ehaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[Activate]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[. If your key is not accepted check that you have entered it exactly as provided, including all dashes. If the problem persists contact PB Software Solutions with your Hardware ID.]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Ehaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&Bitem type = &Epara_start&E/&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Ehaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[My licence key is not being accepted]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&Bitem type = &Epara_start&E/&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[Symptom:]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[ Entering the licence key and clicking Activate shows an Invalid licence key message.]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&Bitem type = &Epara_start&E/&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eebaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[Solution:]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[ Check the following:]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_numbering_level&C1&B/para_numbering_level&C&Bpara_numbering_type&C1&B/para_numbering_type&C&Bpara_first_indent&C40&B/para_first_indent&C&Bpara_full_indent&C40&B/para_full_indent&C&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&Bitem type = &Epara_start&E/&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[Make sure you have copied the key exactly as provided with no extra spaces]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&Bpara_numbering_level&C1&B/para_numbering_level&C&Bpara_numbering_type&C1&B/para_numbering_type&C&Bpara_numbering_keep&C1&B/para_numbering_keep&C&Bpara_first_indent&C40&B/para_first_indent&C&Bpara_full_indent&C40&B/para_full_indent&C&Bpara_style_mask&C-58&B/para_style_mask&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&Bitem type = &Epara_start&E/&C&Bfield id = &E0&E data = &ENO_DATA&E&C&Bfont v=&E2&E h=&E12&E w=&E0&E chs=&E1&E d=&Eeaaaaa&E fc=&ETimes New Roman&E cl=&E0&E bg=&E-1&E si=&E0&E sm=&E-74227&E ss=&Enormal&E&C&Bitem type = &Enormal&E&C&B![CDATA[Make sure you are entering the key on the same computer for which it was generated]]&C&B/item&C&B/font&C&B/field&C&B/p&C&G&Bp v=&E2&E&C&G&B